data.text: @cloudymamma Ahh congratulations that’s brilliant news,  I did another today and will very positive take care of each other
@BrownieLB_1 She’s just heard she’s passed her final exams… celebrated with another lateral flow! Hopefully you’ll have good antibodies after all this, she’s really struggling too. Take care🤗🤗
@cloudymamma Hope your daughter feels better soon too .. my alarms set every 4hrs for paracetamol it’s the only thing I’ve got to look forward to atm 🥺

@BrownieLB_1 Sounds exactly the same!! 
Poor you, plenty fluids, paracetamol and hope you’re passed the worst now, get well soon 🤞🏻🤗🤗🙋🏼‍♀️
@Joeynoble I’ve been In tears all day today everything hurts .. it’s nasty.!! Thank you so much xx
@rebecca5key Thank you, you and me both
@BrownieLB_1 Been wondering how youre doing sweet? It’s bloody awful isn’t it. Me and hubby were poorly for weeks :( sending get well soon hugs xx
@BrownieLB_1 Oh no I really hope it disappears very soon 💐
